Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.93,0:01:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)\c&H92B7FB&\pos(376,850)}四月6日 綠洲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.83,0:01:25.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的車兩三天內真的能修好嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別是在敷衍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.45,0:01:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨中的單色調
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.59,0:02:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:31.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.19,0:03:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.87,0:04:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好臭 幾天沒洗了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.28,0:04:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,5天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.64,0:04:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洗頭又不能用肥皂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.73,0:04:39.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 起來 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HFACBB7&\pos(1644,1008)\fad(200,0)}四月7日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.44,0:04:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭味飄過來了 你頭發上的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.79,0:04:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要讓我用肥皂洗頭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.78,0:04:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別找借口
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko 你昨天洗澡了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么這么問？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.07,0:05:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你為什么會不知道沒有洗發液了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.57,0:05:05.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛死了 請不要打人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.38,0:05:08.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你的頭上的味道就和花田一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.93,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓人受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.32,0:05:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你能去買嗎 洗發液
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.86,0:05:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花田？ 花田的下面是泥土
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是說我有泥臭味？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.70,0:05:21.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 快去！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.52,0:05:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 你！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個島是我們的地盤
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想從這里過 留下買路錢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:06:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也不想受傷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這鞋不錯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.33,0:06:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.18,0:06:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.19,0:06:15.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你把老子我給惹毛了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.45,0:06:27.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.33,0:06:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起美發廳的話 還有一間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是這的邊好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開店的是個叫Anastacia的外地人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過手藝好 而且是個美女
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.07,0:06:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}如果我不愿意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.54,0:06:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你在耍我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.69,0:07:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你這樣是不是太殘酷了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}好不容易近在咫尺了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.46,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發尖修剪整齊 這樣可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.46,0:07:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你是在想Feliciano的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.98,0:07:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}這種事情...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.09,0:07:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}你已經太痛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.27,0:07:19.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}能讓我為你治愈這個傷痛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.81,0:07:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天見過面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Anastacia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡我的香煙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.24,0:07:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香煙？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.63,0:07:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 讓我老公帶在身上的香煙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.04,0:07:48.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他總是擅自拿去抽
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.79,0:07:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那煙是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.34,0:07:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然沒什么大不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:56.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 你是從哪里來的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.05,0:08:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就會離開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.13,0:08:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.61,0:08:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.06,0:08:51.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天下午1點我去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這只是我的誤解 沒有關系
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.46,0:08:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請在那時離開房間
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}圍著浴巾的男孩開船過來 三個人搶了我的鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.75,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我不是故意不去買的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.27,0:09:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bruno
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.87,0:09:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在聽我說話嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.74,0:09:06.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫是什么時候開始在這里的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.91,0:09:07.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.87,0:09:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這么說你完全沒有在聽我說話嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.87,0:09:13.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是完全...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 洗發液呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.42,0:09:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 完全沒有在聽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.77,0:09:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說了 來了圍著浴巾的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.94,0:09:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢和鞋都被搶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.74,0:09:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以洗發液也沒有買成
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.42,0:09:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫把錢和鞋都扔了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.50,0:09:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種謊可騙不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.08,0:09:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看成年人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.56,0:09:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這么討厭洗頭嗎...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.10,0:09:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 開什么玩笑...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:40.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你在干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.59,0:10:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(1632,1042)}四月8日
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.43,0:10:10.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打算一整天都這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:11.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.78,0:10:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我不好 情緒有點不正常
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不餓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去買點什么吃的吧 還有鞋和洗發液
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.49,0:11:32.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.25,0:11:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是沒來得及出門
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.58,0:11:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.61,0:11:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.57,0:11:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什么要這樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.39,0:11:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這需要理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:48.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.17,0:12:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是太強硬了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.91,0:12:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以說 我不知道你已經結婚了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去理發店也是偶然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.70,0:12:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不覺得那是命運嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得是的 所以來到這里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你沒有在這里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有只言片語就這樣結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.34,0:12:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直非常不安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我... 有喜歡的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.49,0:12:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我也有妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不指這個(婚姻形式)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.81,0:12:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.09,0:12:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜歡你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.08,0:12:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該只有我一個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是卻沒有管你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.85,0:12:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.20,0:13:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我 是不會讓你這樣的女孩子悲傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.52,0:13:12.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字 告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.59,0:13:18.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko Malandro
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.55,0:13:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&HA1EEFC&\pos(1632,1036)}四月9日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.94,0:13:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是洗頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.25,0:13:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 別亂動
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.44,0:14:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:12.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.84,0:14:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關系真好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.35,0:14:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母親嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 我也覺得
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們常說 越是吵架關系越好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.63,0:14:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.88,0:14:37.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.86,0:14:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過大家都這么說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過阿姨我們家 一直都沒有吵過架 關系很好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.48,0:14:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有問這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:58.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去 在這里的水面上有悠然游弋的魚兒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.60,0:15:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不受任何拘束 自由地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:07.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得你就像那些魚 很美麗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和這樣的你一起游弋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.13,0:15:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你... 想做什么...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.19,0:15:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我... 該怎么做...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.87,0:15:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:32.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(332,1036)}四月10日
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.05,0:15:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.44,0:15:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在想 是不是可以再更加自由地游弋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說 沒有必要被一片海洋一直束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.95,0:15:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.85,0:15:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什么呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.90,0:15:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是 像魚兒一樣更加自由地游弋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.55,0:15:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么 花心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.22,0:16:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太囂張！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你急什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像傻瓜一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.89,0:16:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi由我一個人去找
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.48,0:16:22.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你... 你在說什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人去找 怎么找？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.77,0:16:25.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.43,0:16:27.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人也能行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.80,0:16:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不需要 不需要Michiko這樣的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.10,0:16:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.98,0:16:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.88,0:16:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 Michiko
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.81,0:17:00.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把搶我的鞋和錢還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.94,0:17:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我比賽！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.73,0:17:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是羅嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.85,0:17:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個還給你也可以 不過你贏得了我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.02,0:17:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣的根本不是我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:14.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.66,0:17:18.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這個丟到水里 先拿到的獲勝 可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.15,0:17:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.26,0:17:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是我贏了的話 那個包就歸我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.55,0:17:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就要這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.51,0:17:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.41,0:17:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.23,0:17:48.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這鞋適合那個孩子 所以拿來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么知道我住這里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在前臺問的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:00.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外還有什么方法嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.52,0:18:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.54,0:18:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么請替我向那個孩子問好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.79,0:18:35.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想和Bruno在一起嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.95,0:18:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.79,0:18:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.44,0:18:42.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以置信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:45.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為我是什么程度的女人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:48.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.24,0:18:51.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得這次也是以往一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.48,0:18:53.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞到手后就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.20,0:18:57.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去性趣 冷淡分手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.10,0:19:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了這種男人 你能舍棄一切嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己... 你自己又怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.35,0:19:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.45,0:19:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然Bruno覺得自己是垂釣者之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.57,0:19:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實他是魚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.82,0:19:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終還是想被我釣到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以問一個問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.18,0:19:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他哪里好？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:28.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“對不起 果然船還是不能給你”
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.39,0:20:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛滿10歲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.00,0:20:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 恭喜！
